OL,3,CConsumer caution ahead of Budget
OL,4,Cdrives drop in footfall ` BRC
OL,6,FLow consumer confidence ahead of a
OL,7,Fpotential tax-rising Budget kept many
OL,8,Fshoppers away from retail locations in
OL,9,FSeptember, according to latest figures.
OL,11,FTube strikes in London, heavy rainfall
OL,12,Fin the first half of September and
OL,13,FStorm Amy towards the end of the month
OL,14,Fexacerbated the decline, the British
OL,15,FRetail Consortium (BRC) said.
OL,17,FTotal UK footfall was down by 1.8% in
OL,18,FSeptember on a year ago, significantly
OL,19,Fmore than the 0.4% decline registered
OL,20,Fin August, BRC-Sensormatic data shows.
