OL,3,CConsumer caution ahead of Budget
OL,4,Cdrives drop in footfall ` BRC
OL,6,FHigh street footfall decreased by 2.5%
OL,7,Fyear on year in September while visits
OL,8,Fto retail parks and shopping centres
OL,9,Fwere down 0.8% and 2% respectively.
OL,11,FFootfall fell year on year across all
OL,12,Fnations again, down 0.5% in Northern
OL,13,FIreland, 1.8% in England, 2.3% in
OL,14,FScotland and the largest decrease of
OL,15,F2.5% in Wales.
