OL,3,CConsumer caution ahead of Budget
OL,4,Cdrives drop in footfall ` BRC
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Retailers' ability to invest in
OL,8,Flocal communities and high streets has
OL,9,Fbeen hampered by last year's budget,
OL,10,Fwhich added #5 billion in employment
OL,11,Fcosts to the industry, in addition to
OL,12,Fa new packaging tax.
OL,14,F"For retailers to invest in shopping
OL,15,Fdestinations that will entice shoppers
OL,16,Fback, the Government-imposed cost
OL,17,Fburdens holding back that investment
OL,18,Fmust be lifted.
