OL,3,CConsumer caution ahead of Budget
OL,4,Cdrives drop in footfall ` BRC
OL,6,F"The upcoming Budget is the moment for
OL,7,Fthe Chancellor to do just that,
OL,8,Fdeliver the Labour manifesto
OL,9,Fcommitment of a meaningful reduction
OL,10,Fin business rates for the industry and
OL,11,Fensure no shop pays more in the
OL,12,Fprocess."
OL,14,FAndy Sumpter, from Sensormatic, said:
OL,15,F"The month began with a modest uplift,
OL,16,Fdriven by back-to-school shopping, but
OL,17,Fmomentum was quickly disrupted.
