OL,3,CConsumer caution ahead of Budget
OL,4,Cdrives drop in footfall ` BRC
OL,6,F"London's Tube strikes mid-month and
OL,7,FStorm Amy at the end brought
OL,8,Fwidespread disruption, impacting
OL,9,Fshopper activity nationwide.
OL,11,F"These events compounded an already
OL,12,Fcautious consumer mood, with many
OL,13,Fstill navigating cost pressures and
OL,14,Feconomic uncertainty.
OL,16,F"Retailers will now be hoping that
OL,17,FSeptember's slowdown was less a sign
OL,18,Fof retreat and more a pause for
OL,19,Fthought."
